{"color":210,"icon":211},[72,236,237],{},"Deleting a tier automatically cancels all subscriptions tied to it immediately.",[72,239,240],{},"If you want to delete a subscription so that no one can use or buy it anymore, simply click the trash icon on the tier card.",{"title":242,"searchDepth":243,"depth":243,"links":244},"",2,[245,246,247,248,249],{"id":83,"depth":243,"text":84},{"id":103,"depth":243,"text":104},{"id":205,"depth":243,"text":206},{"id":224,"depth":243,"text":225},{"id":231,"depth":243,"text":232},"All information on how you can manage tiers.","md",null,{},true,{"title":42,"description":250},[257,259],{"title":38,"path":39,"stem":40,"description":258,"children":-1},"Everything you need to know about creating and editing posts.",{"title":46,"path":47,"stem":48,"description":260,"children":-1},"This document provides comprehensive information on how we handle coupons, which act as promotional codes that fans can use when subscribing to a tier. Coupons can be customized to fit specific needs.",1737121677755]